        Clause 7 <span class="italic">[Interpretation]</span>:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0577P0-02659'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0577P0_19970120_GCR_141' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">The Earl of Lindsay</span> moved Amendment No. 25:
        <q>Page 3, line 30, at end insert&#x2014;</q>
        <q>(""crofting interests" in relation to any property, means the persons with an interest in the property&#x2014;</q>
        <ol>
        <li>(a) as tenants: or</li>
        </ol>
        <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_30gc' title='Col. 30GC &mdash; HL Deb 20 January 1997 vol 577 c30GC' name='column_30gc' href='#column_30gc' rel='bookmark'>30GC</a>
