      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0577P0-02660'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0577P0_19970120_GCR_142' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The noble Earl said: I spoke to this when moving Amendment No. 4A. I beg to move.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0577P0-02661'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0577P0_19970120_GCR_143' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendment agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0577P0-02662'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0577P0_19970120_GCR_144' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 7, as amended, agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0577P0-02663'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0577P0_19970120_GCR_145' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Remaining clause agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0577P0-02664'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0577P0_19970120_GCR_146' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Title agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0577P0-02665'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0577P0_19970120_GCR_147' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Bill reported with amendments.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0577P0-02666'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0577P0_19970120_GCR_148' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at twenty-five minutes past six o'clock.
      </p>
